data.description: Nestled in prestigious Armonk, this custom-built Stone Manor Home boasts impeccable craftsmanship and elegant design. Featuring a grand open concept with two floating circle stairs, it offers a lavish two-story living room, heated flooring, and a gourmet kitchen flowing into inviting gathering spaces. Outside, a stone patio with fireplace and expansive backyard await, perfect for entertaining and soccer matches. Tucked behind a gated entry lies a nearly 5-acre private oasis, ideal for a future pool. Luxuries abound, including dual primary suites, six full bathrooms, and a remarkable lower level with office, fireplace, movie theater, and wine cellar. This home embodies luxury living with its heated kitchen and bathroom floors, along with a heated three-car garage. Minutes to the town of Armonk, shops and main roads.   Seven miles from the North White Plains train station, 35 miles from New York City, and conveniently located to Westchester Airport.  The Byram Hills School District a Blue Ribbon Award Winner.
